sequenceDiagram
accTitle: Mermaid actor boxes
accDescr {
Demonstrates Mermaid participant boxes mapped onto sequencer actor groups, including adjacent different-colour boxes and a repeated Data tier box ending on Audit.
From the project root, regenerate this Mermaid transform and SVG with:
node sequencer.js --mermaid -i test/mermaid-features/19-box-actor-groups/input.mmd -o -f -t test/mermaid-features/19-box-actor-groups
}
box Aqua Client tier
  participant Caller
  participant Browser
end
box rgba(255, 230, 200, 0.55) Data tier
  participant DB
  participant Cache
end
participant Service
box rgba(255, 230, 200, 0.55) Data tier
  participant Audit
end
Caller->>Service: Start request [Mermaid: Caller->>Service: Start request]
Service->>DB: Persist record [Mermaid: Service->>DB: Persist record]
Service->>Cache: Prime cache [Mermaid: Service->>Cache: Prime cache]
Service->>Audit: Record audit [Mermaid: Service->>Audit: Record audit]
